I heard paar chanaa de 6 years ago and have always tried to feel the emotions of Sonni and Mahiwaal. Every time I feel like I have got it now, It seems as if I get to feel more things each time I search for this. Today, I am broken more than ever and I seem to get more of the emotions of Mahiwal. 
Beautiful it is, Yaar nu milegi aaj laash yaar di😊
